    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presenting an investment-grade vehicle that redefines the standard for pre-owned excellence. This exceptional example is offered in true mint condition, having undergone a rigorous multi-point inspection to ensure mechanical and aesthetic perfection. The exterior retains its original showroom luster, while the cabin remains in a pristine, untouched state. For the discerning buyer seeking a vehicle that bridges the gap between pre-owned and brand new, this remains an unparalleled opportunity. Performance, luxury, and absolute peace of mind converge in this singular offering.",
      "price": 48900.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
